---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Books";
const description = "Long-form work extending beyond the page.";
---

<Layout
  title={title}
  description={description}
>
  <section class="books-page" data-pagefind-body>

    <h1>Exit Wounds</h1>

    <div class="book-intro">
      <div class="book-copy">
        <p>
          <em>Exit Wounds</em> was written while my life was coming apart. Some of these poems were written in motel rooms. Some were written in treatment. Some were written sitting in parked cars trying to decide what to do next. A lot of this book was written before I had enough distance to explain any of it correctly. The poems still carry confusion, exhaustion, attachment, denial, relief, shame, hope, and all the other contradictions I was living inside at the time. Nothing here was written with the benefit of hindsight. That would have been a different book.
        </p>
        <p>
          For a deeper look at the thinking behind the work, see <a href="/writing/exit-wounds" title="Exit Wounds">the accompanying post</a>.
        </p>

        <br />

        <h2>Excerpt</h2>
        <blockquote class="poem">
          You called it a bond.
          <br /><br />
          I call it a house made of mirrors,
          <br />
          every room shaped like your absence.
          <br /><br />
          A devotion with a detonator
          <br />
          tucked inside a kiss.
          <br /><br />
          The worst thing you ever did
          <br />
          was make me apologize
          <br />
          for drowning in water
          <br />
          you swore wasn’t there,
          <br />
          from a well you never meant to fill.
        </blockquote>
        <p class="citation">From “Exit Wounds”</p>
      </div>

      <div class="book-cover">
        <img
          src="/images/writing/exit-wounds-bookcover.png"
          alt="Exit Wounds book cover"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <br />

    <h2>Availability</h2>
    <p>
      Available as hardcover, paperback, and eBook through Amazon.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://a.co/d/0epExT7s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Available on Amazon →
      </a>
    </p>

    <br />

    <p>
      Signed copies are available <a href="mailto:hello@amidthenoise.com">by request</a>.
    </p>

  </section>
</Layout>
<style>
  .book-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 280px;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-block: 1rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .book-cover img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .book-copy h2 {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .book-copy h2 + .poem {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .book-intro {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .book-cover {
      max-width: 320px;
    }
  }
</style>